  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Say thank you to someone at Companies House
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Send an email to say thanks for the excellent service or help you've received from a person or team at Companies House.</p>

  </div>
